位就咁拉條線去主線位，搞到嗰度勁亂，同一個位有4條線，1 input (from outside)+ 3 output(to rooms and other lan slot)<br />\n<br />\n第二張圖唔要紅線就係我本身用58u 嘅setting，<br />\n而家換返之前隻垃圾tplink當modem用住先，藍色係主線，三條黃色入房，紅色就係後加駁返隻58U放wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家成個感覺好白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d408ce7533ac230c15e8cbbb88fdb3c2a5a944","tid":588073,"uid":61071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>尋晚買左部AC58U，返到屋企set up完用左陣都無事<br />\n但之後開始間歇性斷線，成部機得 power 有著光，其他(2.4GHz &amp; 5GHz etc.)全部熄哂燈，<br />\n無過熱，但係所有Lan線 Wifi 都斷哂完全上唔到網<br />\n要隔一陣佢先會著返其他燈&amp; 回復正常<br />\n<br />\n關唔關Fw事？<br />\n有無爸打知點解/可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>有冇試過唔插router?</blockquote>我因為之前屋企裝修有啲問題 師傅無拉好線位 而家一定要駁Modem/Router拉上網入房<br />\n又無買Modem，所以唯有直接駁Router</blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/161425_bc44d5e8cd43780bf5a22a72306edb65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F161425_bc44d5e8cd43780bf5a22a72306edb65.png&h=3bd56a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/161434_fa3bce032fe801bedf0f1a69057f97d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F161434_fa3bce032fe801bedf0f1a69057f97d7.png&h=9551a1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一張圖係HKBN就咁拉左條線入屋既主線位，之後我搵返裝修個師傅駁返入房，佢就咁喺其他要插lan既牆位就咁拉條線去主線位，搞到嗰度勁亂，同一個位有4條線，1 input (from outside)+ 3 output(to rooms and other lan slot)<br />\n<br />\n第二張圖唔要紅線就係我本身用58u 嘅setting，<br />\n而家換返之前隻垃圾tplink當modem用住先，藍色係主線，三條黃色入房，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最右上</strong></span>嗰條線就係後加駁返隻58U放wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家成個感覺好白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"064e4a8